        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Isaboko's bridal design reflects the thoughtful, one-of-a-kind approach found in all our work. We will work with you to bring your vision to life. Whether you are looking for a gown made from your family material archive, a series of bridal party gifts, or a custom tapestry for your wedding arch, we can help.</p><p>We specialize in incorporating vintage materials into custom bridal pieces\u2014whether it's a family kimono, vintage lace, or other meaningful textiles. These materials carry history and memory, transformed into something new to wear on your most important day.</p><p>Our approach is slow, intentional, and deeply personal.</p><p><a href=\"mailto:hello@isaboko.com\">hello@isaboko.com</a></p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
